### =====================================================================
### AppSettings API  (base route: api/AppSettings/)
### =====================================================================
@host = http://localhost:5000
@apiKey = your-dev-api-key
@token =

### Read - returns ApiCallCosts + ChargeInternet config
POST {{host}}/api/AppSettings/Read
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}"
}
